<p><a name="Books" id="Books"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Granular_synthesis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Books">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFRoads2001">Roads, Curtis (2001). <i>Microsound</i>. Cambridge: MIT Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0262182157" class="internal">ISBN 0-262-18215-7</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Microsound&amp;rft.aulast=Roads&amp;rft.aufirst=Curtis&amp;rft.au=Roads%2C+Curtis&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.place=Cambridge&amp;rft.pub=MIT+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-262-18215-7&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Granular_synthesis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFMiranda2002">Miranda, E. R. (2002). <i>Computer Sound Design: Synthesis Techniques and Programming</i>. Oxford: Focal Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0240516931" class="internal">ISBN 0-240-51693-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Computer+Sound+Design%3A+Synthesis+Techniques+and+Programming&amp;rft.aulast=Miranda&amp;rft.aufirst=E.+R.&amp;rft.au=Miranda%2C+E.+R.&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.place=Oxford&amp;rft.pub=Focal+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-240-51693-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Granular_synthesis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.artesonoro.net/tesisgran/indicegran.html" class="external text" title="http://www.artesonoro.net/tesisgran/indicegran.html" rel="nofollow">"Les techniques granulares dans la synthèse sonore</a> by Manuel Rocha Iturbide. Doctoral Thesis. University of Paris VIII, Paris France, 1999.</li>
</ul>
