<p><a name="Articles" id="Articles"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Granular_synthesis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Articles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Articles</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://music.calarts.edu/~eric/gs.html" class="external text" title="http://music.calarts.edu/~eric/gs.html" rel="nofollow">Granular Synthesis</a> by Eric Kuehnl</li>
<li><a href="http://artesonoro.net/articulos/The%20development%20of%20GiST.pdf" class="external text" title="http://artesonoro.net/articulos/The%20development%20of%20GiST.pdf" rel="nofollow">"The development of GiST, a Granular. Synthesis Toolkit Based on an Extension of the FOF Generator"</a> by Gerhard Eckel and <a href="/wiki/Manuel_Rocha_Iturbide" title="Manuel Rocha Iturbide">Manuel Rocha Iturbide</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.artesonoro.net/tesisgran/portadagran.html" class="external text" title="http://www.artesonoro.net/tesisgran/portadagran.html" rel="nofollow">Searching for a global synthesis technique through a quantum conception of sound</a> by Manuel Rocha Iturbide</li>
<li><a href="http://emusician.com/software/going-with-grain/" class="external text" title="http://emusician.com/software/going-with-grain/" rel="nofollow">Going with the Grain</a> a review of 10 granular synthesis programs by Dennis Miller (2008)</li>
</ul>
